<L>__{exterior street morning}
<A>__{ben is leaving his home. this is a saturday morning. two men are sitting in a car a few yards from the entrance to the house. ben doesn't pay attention to them. when he is about twenty yards past, one of the men, jaimie who was present when gordon was arrested gets out of the car and follows ben. ben stops at a corner for a car and again the footsteps stop. he turns furtively and sees the man, stopped, turning his head. ben decides to turn the corner, and listens to the footsteps. the man is still following. ben then decides to turn right back to have a good look at the man. they pass each other and ben takes a good look at him and turns back onto the streets to the local shops. the man decides not to follow.}
